{
  "stem": "107.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was unusual, because usually that hospitals are the ones that go first.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never quite understood, but the-- our assumption and some of the interpretation we heard from people who-- who knew more than we knew said it was a fight between Mengele and-- and the head of the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew it, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- he had the right to say I have the commander from Berlin to liquidate the camp [INAUDIBLE], and Mengele was saying, but not my hospital.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wasn't fond of it, but it was a matter of-- of power.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- I cannot swear that that is the explanation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he had some interest in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know him as well as one of the people standing there when he comes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had never anything to do with me, or I had never anything to do with him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was cold like ice, and he assumed-- I am sure he assumed what he was doing was in the interest of the movement of creating a big, German, powerful, imperial, with no foreign blood, which is a strange concept-- would find any rights or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say always that he was totally detached.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, when he puts this psychotic, the manic patient, who was a lovely young man, send him to be executed, that was just like you sent another patient for surgery.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no particular-- I mean, I have never seen him [INAUDIBLE] with newcomers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I have seen pictures, and I know and have listened to people who where there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- he did it as a duty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is no excuse, of course, but of course he was also very clever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He knew how to save himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
